room_title: Escape room "Nonna's House" by Ocean State Escape in Providence
room_description:
Something is wrong when Nonna doesn’t invite you over for Sunday dinner.

You always knew she was a fan of an occasional trip to the local casino, but when you arrive at Nonna’s you find her gambling habit was a bit bigger than you realized. Nonna is in trouble and you have one hour to help set things right to get her back…
